### ============================
### ORDERS
### ============================

# Listar todos os pedidos
GET http://localhost:8080/orders
Authorization: Basic admin 123456

###

# Criar novo pedido
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic admin 123456

{
  "status": "PENDING",
  "total": 199.90,
  "user": { "id": 1 },
  "product": { "id": 1 }
}

###

# Atualizar pedido
PUT http://localhost:8080/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic admin 123456

{
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "total": 199.90,
  "user": { "id": 1 },
  "product": { "id": 1 }
}

###

# Deletar pedido
DELETE http://localhost:8080/orders/1
Authorization: Basic admin 123456
